Microsoft learn -> best way to learn microsoft technologies
Why take the exam : It forces you to learn the technology in side out.
3 differnt exams.
1, AZ-900 (Optional)Fundamentals exam - entry level (optional)
2, AZ-203 Assosiate - next level ( Admin or Developer ) 
3, Exprert level certification (AZ-400) Microsoft Azure Dev ops
4, Azure expert level architect (you need to pass two exams : Az300 and Az301)


